    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">

      <!-- AI-Friendly Summary -->
      <div class="bg-navy/5 border-l-4 border-gold rounded-r-lg p-4 mb-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed italic">Dolphin Centrifuge supplies purpose-built Oil Recovery Systems (ORS) for crude oil tank bottom processing. This modular 3-step centrifuge system processes tank bottoms with up to 60% BS&W, recovering saleable crude oil with less than 0.5% BS&W. Available in skid-mounted and containerized configurations, the ORS combines a decanter centrifuge for de-sludging (down to 200 microns) and a high-speed disc stack centrifuge for final polishing (down to 1 micron). Based in Warren, Michigan, Dolphin Centrifuge has over 40 years of experience in petroleum centrifugal separation.</p>
