          <div id="roi">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1B3A5C] mb-3">Crude Oil Recovery -- ROI Calculation</h4>
            <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed mb-3">
              Using the process flow rates above, some preliminary ROI calculations follow. The return on investment has been calculated based on 3 different crude oil market prices per barrel.
            </p>
            <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Based on the conservative expectation of about 25% crude oil recovery, it is easy to see our Oil Recovery System's short payback period.
            </p>

            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
              <table class="w-full text-sm text-[#2D2D2D] border-collapse">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="bg-[#1B3A5C] text-white">
                    <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">% Oil In Tank Bottom</th>
